reviews.text: Quiet environment. Spacious seating. Good for friends gathering. The dim sum dishes in general were delicious and tasty. There were lots of traditional and fusion food. The pork liver dumplings however were a bit lousy, overcooked and tasteless. The fish maw soup dumplings were the best. Love this restaurant by the harbour. Not too crowded. Will come back again.
Nice food! Must try the cod fish with rice cracker! Very good service and friendly staff! Restaurant location is good and you can enjoy the harbor view!

The Lobster Noodle (龍蝦伊麵）is really delicious.  The five years Shaoxing wine（古越龍山花雕）tasted great and matched well with seafood. The restaurant is located in the tourist spot near the Star Ferry in Kowloon.  Friday evening is full house and crowded.  Waiters and waitress are short of service.
Food was great esp the egg tarts and the rice rolls! It was not as crowded on a weekday afternoon thus we did not have to wait for a table. Service was prompt too.

Super awesome food. They are quick to prepare order and the place is conveniently located in Avenue of Stars. Recommended for authentic Cantonese food. 

The service could have been better though.

Quiet environment. Spacious seating. Good for friends gathering. The dim sum dishes in general were delicious and tasty. There were lots of traditional and fusion food. The pork liver dumplings however were a bit lousy, overcooked and tasteless. The fish maw soup dumplings were the best. Love this restaurant by the harbour. Not too crowded. Will come back again.
점심 식사하러 들른 딤섬 식당. 홍콩섬이 보이는 전망 좋은 식당이기는 한데.. 창가에서 먼 구석진 안쪽 테이블. 그래도 예전에 유명 딤섬 가게에서 줄서기 귀찮아서 못 먹은 아쉬움을 드디어 달래 본다. 식사하면서 둘러보니 패키지 또는 투어 손님도 많이 오는 것 같고, 결혼식 피로연 장소로도 사용되는 것 같다. 맛은 괜찮은 편..
在此處近窗座位用餐，香港島海景一覽無遺，一邊享用美食，一邊飽覽世界級海港景色，其樂何如。食物精緻美味，價錢尚算合理。
